@san_francisco
subtitle: It will be easier to organize in California due to our established infrastructure there.
on-arrival: independence += 5; youth_democrat -= 1; youth_dove += 4; consumer_dove += 2; consumer_democrat -= 1; california_dove_bonus += 5; oregon_dove_bonus += 2; washington_dove_bonus += 4

California is by far the state with our strongest presence, especially in the Bohemian capital of America, San Francisco. We are quickly able to organize a grand convention, and plaster posters all throughout the hip world of San Francisco. We exceed even our own expectations in attendees, and Eugene McCarthy is greeted by great applause as he arrives in California from Chicago. Even the remaining Diggers have made an appearance, and in the following convention Eugene McCarthy is in a landslide confirmed as the Peace and Freedom Party's nominee, to more thunderous applause from the attendants.

